dataflowSinks.name: UserQuerysink
dataflowSinks.script:
sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	input(
		ID as integer,
		FirstName as string,
		LastName as string
	),
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	errorHandlingOption: 'stopOnFirstError') ~> UserQuerysink
